title: HPV vaccination for teenagers
description:
A vaccine called Gardasil 9 has been developed which can significantly decrease your chance of developing HPV-related cancers and genital warts.

When you are 12–13 years old you can have the HPV vaccine for free at school. Find out more: http://www.hpvvaccine.org.au/
